Health Endpoints (return {"status": "ok"} with 200):

http://localhost:8080/health - Receiver service health
http://localhost:8100/health - Processing service health
http://localhost:8110/health - Analyzer service health
http://localhost:8120/health - Health Check service (returns all service statuses)

Statistics Endpoints:

http://localhost:8100/stats - Processing service statistics
http://localhost:8110/stats - Analyzer service statistics

Event Endpoints (Analyzer):
http://localhost:8110/na_train/passenger_count?index={number} - Get specific passenger count event
http://localhost:8110/na_train/incoming_train?index={number} - Get specific incoming train event

Dashboard:
http://localhost:3000 - Main dashboard displaying health status, statistics, and events

Swagger UI (API Documentation):

http://localhost:8080/ui - Receiver API docs
http://localhost:8100/ui - Processing API docs
http://localhost:8110/ui - Analyzer API docs
http://localhost:8120/ui - Health Check API docs




